title: TWEE Unicorn Horn Sidewalk Chalk
description:
Unicorn horns are always awesome and now you can create magical drawings with them! This set includes three sidewalk chalk horns: one cool horn, one warm horn and one gold and glitter-coated white chalk horn

  • Dimensions: Each horn is 3.5 inches in height and about 1.75 inches in diameter
  • Please note that Twee chalk is intended for sidewalk use, meaning for gritty surfaces as opposed to smooth ones (like chalkboards).

Twee is a woman-owned and operated company based out of Philadelphia.
